lead_paragraph: A Frenchman being involved in a long -- or rather very, very long -- fifth set epic against John Isner at Wimbledon had a feeling of deja vu about it.

headline.print_headline: Tsonga Beats Marathon Man Isner in Another Wimbledon Epic
